snippet.title: Best VGM 1192 - Etrian Odyssey IV - Labyrinth I ~ Cerulean Woodlands
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 2056 - https://youtu.be/TaRAKfltBfo

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Nintendo 3DS
Etrian Odyssey IV (2012)
Labyrinth I ~ Cerulean Woodlands
Yuzo Koshiro
